1
00:00:01,000 --> 00:00:06,000
At 09:14 UTC, checkout latency crossed 900 milliseconds.

2
00:00:07,000 --> 00:00:13,000
错误码 E42 表示缓存写锁未释放，影响了三个工作节点。

3
00:00:14,000 --> 00:00:21,000
The operator ran aurora cache inspect and identified worker-7 as the lock owner.

4
00:00:22,000 --> 00:00:29,000
The lock was cleared under incident INC-204, and latency recovered by 09:22 UTC.
